---
const ghUrl = "https://code.alipay.com/cattery/rotom";
---
<section class="hero section--first">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero__grid">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">A2A WORKSPACE · MESH NETWORK</span>
        <h1 class="hero__title">
          让专业 CLI Agent<br />
          变成可<em>协作</em>的数字员工
        </h1>
        <p class="hero__desc">
          Rotom 是一个中心化的数字员工协作网络。把 claude / codex / openclaw / hermes 等
          专业 CLI 工具封装成数字员工,在浏览器里统一调度、派活、看进度。
          员工自带记忆和技能,定时巡检主动认领任务 —— 你只管提需求,执行交给 Agents。
        </p>
        <div class="hero__cta">
          <a href="#quickstart" class="btn btn--primary">快速开始 →</a>
          <a href={ghUrl} class="btn btn--ghost" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">查看代码</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__stats">
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">1 中枢</div><div class="l">统一调度所有数字员工</div></div>
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">多agent</div><div class="l">claude / codex / hermes / openclaw 同台协作</div></div>
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">记忆 + 技能</div><div class="l">员工越用越懂你</div></div>
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">主动出击</div><div class="l">自动识别可认领任务</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__shot">
        <img src="/rotom.jpeg" alt="Rotom 数字员工 Mesh" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
